Class FinalizedResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.Resource
      • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.FinalizedResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AggregatingFilter, AggregationFunction, CallStatus, ContextEventPattern, FormElement, ManagedIndividual, ProcessResult, ProfileParameter, Property, PropertyPath, RDFClassInfo, ScopedResource, ServiceProfile, ServiceRealization, UIHandlerProfile, Variable

    public class FinalizedResource
extends Resource
    This class finalizes some of the methods of Resource so that they cannot be overwritten by subclasses.
    Author:
    Carsten Stockloew
